invalid type: string "www.novigosolutions.com \nNovigo Solutions Pvt. Ltd.  \nIII. Maternity Leave Policy: \nAll women employees are entitled to maternity benefits as prescribed under the Maternity Benefit \nAct, 1961 prevailing at the time of pregnancy. \n\u{f0b7} Women employees are eligible for maternity benefit only if they have worked for a minimum \nperiod of 80 days in thecompany. \n\nn \n 